itunes:title: 174. Andy & DJ CTI: Young Dolph, Rittenhouse Not Guilty and Austrian Police & Army Standing Up To Government
description: In today's episode, Andy and DJ discuss the passing of Young Dolph in his own community, Kyle Rittenhouse being found not guilty on all counts, and the Austrian Police & Army standing with their people against the government's "health dictatorship" mandates.
